@startuml

title Skills Pattern - Composable Agent Capabilities

skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor #E8F5E9
    BorderColor #2E7D32
}

skinparam package {
    BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    BorderColor #616161
}

actor "User" as User

component "Agent" as Agent
component "Skill Router" as Router

package "Skill Registry" as Registry {
    component "Code Skill" as CodeSkill
    component "Research Skill" as ResearchSkill
    component "Data Analysis Skill" as DataSkill
    component "Communication Skill" as CommSkill
}

package "Skill Resources" as Resources {
    database "Code Repos" as Repos
    database "Knowledge Base" as KB
    database "Data Sources" as Data
    collections "APIs" as APIs
}

User --> Agent : Complex request
Agent --> Router : Analyze & route

Router --> CodeSkill : Code tasks
Router --> ResearchSkill : Information gathering
Router --> DataSkill : Analytics tasks
Router --> CommSkill : Output formatting

CodeSkill --> Repos : Read/Write code
ResearchSkill --> KB : Search documents
DataSkill --> Data : Query & analyze
CommSkill --> APIs : Send notifications

CodeSkill --> Router : Code artifacts
ResearchSkill --> Router : Research findings
DataSkill --> Router : Analysis results
CommSkill --> Router : Formatted output

Router --> Agent : Combined results
Agent --> User : Synthesized response

note right of Registry
  Skills are:
  * Self-contained
  * Composable
  * Reusable
  * Specialized
end note

note bottom of Router
  Router handles:
  * Skill selection
  * Parallel execution
  * Result aggregation
end note

@enduml
